ffected by remote sensing. We demonstrate that spectral plant-trait alterations caused by X. fastidiosa infection are detectable previsually at the landscape scale, a critical requirement to help eradicate some of the most devastating plant diseases worldwide.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Zarco-Tejada, P. J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Camino, C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Beck, P. S. A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Calderon, R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hornero, A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hern\u00e1ndez-Clemente, R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kattenborn, T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Montes-Borrego, M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Susca, L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Morelli, M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gonzalez-Dugo, V.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "North, P. R. J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Landa, B. B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Boscia, D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Saponari, M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Navas-Cortes, J. A.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 5", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/7cba3ac825e939388bc1c42706ada7c8", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/5dfad606da7b707d8022929ee89f1834b953ca016f082cb73fbe71a2cc5d8fcd", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/KSCBICZW", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/KSCBICZW", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/2856c658a635daf344f7958f785111e8!/b104256-106400", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "